I am a 48-year-old Scottish/Irish woman who loves housekeeping and cooking. I enjoy doing domestic work and am very conscientious, meticulous and organized.

I currently work as a live-in housekeeper for a British gentleman near Mies and am responsible for keeping the house and large terrace clean and tidy, as well as doing all the shopping.

I previously worked as a property manager for an eight-bedroom villa near Cannes where I provide a full housekeeping service for a HNW family of four (one parent and three teenage girls). I also maintained the security of the property while the family were in Monaco and liaised with external contractors who carried out extensive renovation works to the property.

I have a quiet and flexible personality and am used to managing my workload to make sure that everything gets done on time. I am organised and responsible and able to use my initiative when needed. 

I am a native English-speaker and speak French to A’ Level standard. 

I am very interested in this job and do hope you will consider my application.

Kind regards,

